{
  "stem": "2916.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was like a very social place, our store.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have very, very happy memories of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Many of the farmers-- it was a farming community-- would come in and the farmers' wives.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I would know everybody intimately and their children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They would sit sometimes for hours, sometimes not even on chairs, but on sacks of animal feed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had all kinds of sacks with barley and wheat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] oh, I can't remember all the names of the various grains that were in large sacks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And as the sack was getting lower and lower, it was very convenient to sit on and people would sit and-- and just chat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, and these were all not Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were all gentiles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I never knew the difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I didn't even know I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I just grew up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were Orthodox Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're observing all the Jewish laws and customs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that didn't tell me that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know to the extent that I have a recollection that my mother told me later, that she overheard me while she was in the store.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was right in front talking to one of my friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I must have been about five.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And her-- my friend said, you know, the Jew came today to us to buy a goose.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, the local Jews were not called the Jew by these children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was a Jew from probably another town who came to look for geese or chickens or for other farm goods.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he wore a beard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You see, all the Jews in our town did not have beards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a strictly Orthodox community, but all the men were clean shaven.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
